Comment: 0,0:24:25.73,0:24:27.73,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,*Gundam Takemikazuchi, moving out!*
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:08.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\fnKandide Upper Wide\shad0\b0\bord0\blur0.8\fs60\fscx120\pos(1229,603)}ECHO IN THE BLUE SKY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:10.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A large battalion of the Roman Army\Nappeared on the border of Seize?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:35.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that gunshot just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:41.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The Roman soldier has been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:43.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:45.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Our unit will now rendezvous with the 1st and 3rd Divisions\Nthat are heading to the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:53.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:54.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:56.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If you move, I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:58.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:05.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel, order your men to retreat from the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:11.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}What in the world is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}It's treason!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:16.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}The girls in the fortress took our commander hostage\Nand locked themselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:18.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:23.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Luckily, it didn't hit her internal organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:24.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:26.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}I don't think her life is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Thank you, Yumina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:32.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:36.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl was to be a sacrifice for the battle, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:38.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd be worth less if she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:39.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:49.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been trailing the Roman Army moving along\Nthe rear border of our country for the past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:53.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably their way of putting pressure on the peace talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They underestimated us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:02:00.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Archduke was being a coward,\Ntelling us not to do anything to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:05.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we need a way to force them\Nto make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:10.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, the execution of a\Ncrying captive in front of their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:12.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't possibly{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The peace talks are a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We must burn Rome to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:20.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Kannagi Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:23.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, our famous "Helvetian Witch".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think I didn't recognize you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:31.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Noel was just used by you people!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:37.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So you really had something to do\Nwith that Invisible Reaper after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:39.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The Invisible Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:43.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Known as the genius born only once in a century,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:49.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who revived the Invisible Reaper\Nat a bioweapons facility from the old era,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:51.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,is that girl over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Your talent is valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:09.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,take this man to the underground distillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:14.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,My armies should be deploying\Nto confront the Romans as I speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation just needs a small spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're back to the battlefield again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I thought it was all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Our luck sucks, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:32.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I have confined the Colonel in the distillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have some of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought these baked sweets from Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:49.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They're good, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san, you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get out if it gets really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This all is just messed up, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire maidens are supposed to protect the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:06.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but we end up getting the town involved in our war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:15.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,While we were hiding, Aisha-san told me\Nabout the legend of the fire maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:18.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And she said, according to the Roman literature,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:22.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,they tell a completely different version of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:27.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire maidens protect lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:51.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn to take watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you even handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:59.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the resolution to shoot someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:06.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If I believe it's the right thing to do, I think I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:11.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am a girl of the fortress after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:14.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like our great seniors, the fire maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:20.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You really believe that fairy-tale story\Ncreated by the Romans?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I can understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire maidens protect lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that might be the case, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:36.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hear what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:06:00.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she can hear that all the way out here,\Nno matter how good her ears are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A ceasefire call?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still early to rejoice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She might have misheard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:20.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if she's right, it's still unclear\Nwhether the peace treaty was signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to inform Colonel Hopkins{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:28.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,When I brought the Colonel his meal, he wasn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We will begin our assault in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:45.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think the Colonel will listen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't hurt to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:57.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colonel... was laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:07:03.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing the death and destruction caused by the Reaper I revived,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,he laughed hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He... will kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He will fight until no one is left alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:18.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I helped him with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you think,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:25.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,then please, save more people than you have killed, Noel-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:31.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ceasefire you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can trust her ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We can guarantee that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:44.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a scatterbrain, she forgets stuff,\Nacts like a kid, and isn't sexy at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but she wouldn't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Detain this old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want war that badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:55.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Civilization and science progress through war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:08:00.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to recreate the past glory of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:07.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the Roman Army is planning to attack tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:12.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we can no longer avoid battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san has been detained.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:30.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against The Demon of Vingt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:37.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want the notes that have been entrusted to me get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:40.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just you! You're being selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you deciding everything yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're soldiers, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:50.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone once told me that the world has already come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:54.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I love his world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I love all of you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Aisha-san wants as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've killed other people too, as a soldier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:31.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like you, Noel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:39.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:44.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just... Like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've suffered enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You've suffered enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:53.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I forgive you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:58.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...even if no one else will forgive you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, it's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go, there's no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:51.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... there's nothing more for me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:03.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been holding out for our sake, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:14.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want a girl my age... to go through... torture too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Rio-senpai's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:23.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And Noel and Kanata are such slackers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:28.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... I need to be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:32.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I couldn't be a reliable Captain for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:42.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please God,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:48.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,give your blessings to these fire maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Raising the main conversion reactor output.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:04.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,FAP, FAC, DMR, ECP operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:07.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Superconductor circuit is stabilizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire control system is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:14.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The main cannon as well as secondary cannon are functional.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Release all joint locks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:23.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Weight reduction system, operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:26.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Coefficient minus, around five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparations complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it just like we practiced and we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, my darlings!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:38.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare the main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Load AP round!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,AP round loaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:51.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Target ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan, the call please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"Commence assault"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:16.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kanata nee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemikazuchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:14:00.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They've rebuilt that much of the old era technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal to all tanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Move out and stop them at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch the assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No more war!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:14.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way you'll get through is over our dead bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:15.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:19.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your next move, Mr. Demon of Vingt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:36.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Circle around! Rendezvous with the rear forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:45.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire maidens protect lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:50.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to you, Kanata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:00.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,before the world became what it is today,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:06.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,an angel was sent down by God\Nto deliver punishment unto the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:11.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It got injured and rested its wings at the western end of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:22.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who saved the angel were maidens\Nliving in the fortress on the outskirts of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:27.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They knew it was sent to destroy them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:32.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but, upon seeing the pitiful wounded angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:38.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,the maidens, with the help of a giant spider,\Ngave the angel shelter at the bottom of the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:47.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The maidens took turns holding the angel's neck,\Nlaboring to suppress the flowing blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:54.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the angel gave to the maidens\Na golden horn in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:16:01.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in the end, the townspeople found out about the angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:04.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and set fire to the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:13.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The maidens were engulfed in flames, the angel beheaded and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:23.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, the angel's army descended and shrouded the sky over the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:26.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It may have been a miracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:32.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but a note resounded through the sky,\Nand the angels drew back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:38.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Saving all the human lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:45.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,was the sound of a golden horn,\Nblown by the last maiden, in exchange for her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:00.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you remember that Missy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The one you gave your caramel to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:07.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be dragged into this, won't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, prepare for attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:13.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all soldiers. It's our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:29.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:33.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tank of an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:40.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The unit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ceasefire call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Roman military's call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell we'll stop here! Prepare the main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're not stopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:27.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:17.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Start firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:20.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, lower your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:40.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the second heir of the Helvetian Royal Republic,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:43.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and the fiancée of the Holy Roman Emperor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio Kazumiya Arkadia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:53.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I command you in the name of my father, the Archduke of Helvetia, and the Roman Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The treaty is signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall not fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:21:00.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Both sides shall disengage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:02.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an imperial order!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:10.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who act in defiance shall be punished by the First Helvetian Royal Guard in the name of both leaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:53.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Missy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Missy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:21:59.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeants!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:30.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very much spring now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:32.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Noel...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:37.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Aisha write in her letter the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:41.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wounds have healed well, and now each day I practice{\fscx300}-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:43.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Translate, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:45.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's all better now and practicing her trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:48.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Good for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:55.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We get a letter from Rome, but not from the Government Center, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.43,0:22:57.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:22:59.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's a princess and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:05.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, she was completely surrounded by guards on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:07.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,so we couldn't talk to her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:10.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I hear the sound of Claus-san's bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:19.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here! She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:22.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this new recruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:24.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be strict and{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:48.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, I am assigned to Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.23,0:23:50.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Rio Kazumiya Arkadia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:54.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Filicia Heidemann, permission to be posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.87,0:23:56.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Permission granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:59.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't use ranks here, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:06.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, the Roman emperor turned out to be quite understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:12.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd grant me one wish as a reward for stopping the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:15.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:20.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:21.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:23.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.56,0:24:24.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.35,0:24:26.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Rio.
